MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1248. S.N. v. M.B.

Franklin App. No. 09AP-1021, 2010-Ohio-2479. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

*1526It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
